'''中国甲龙'''（[[属名|属名]]：''Sinankylosaurus''，意为“中国融合蜥蜴”）是[[中国|中国]][[山东省|山东省]][[白垩纪|晚白垩世]][[甲龙类|甲龙类]][[恐龙|恐龙]]的一个[[属|属]]。该属包含单一物种'''诸城中国甲龙'''（''Sinankylosaurus zhuchengensis''），所知于一个近乎完整的右[[髂骨|髂骨]]。叙述者解释说，中国甲龙的发现不仅扩大了对诸城恐龙种类的认识，也显示了[[东亚|东亚]]和[[北美|北美]]恐龙的相似性。<ref name=Wang2020>{{cite journal|last1=Wang|first1=K. B.|last2=Zhang|first2=Y. X.|last3=Chen|first3=J.|last4=Chen|first4=S. Q.|last5=Wang|first5=P. Y.|year=2020|title=A new ankylosaurian from the Late Cretaceous strata of Zhucheng, Shandong Province|url=http://dzhtb.cgs.cn/gbcen/ch/reader/create_pdf.aspx?file_no=20200703&flag=1&year_id=2020&quarter_id=7|journal=Geological Bulletin of China|language=zh|volume=39|issue=7|pages=958–962|access-date=2020-11-21|archive-date=2020-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200913051834/http://dzhtb.cgs.cn/gbcen/ch/reader/create_pdf.aspx?file_no=20200703&flag=1&year_id=2020&quarter_id=7|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==发现与命名==
进入21世纪后，从1964年开始古生物学家在诸城进行了大规模的发掘，发现了丰富的化石资源，特别是恐龙化石。<ref>[https://paleobiodb.org/classic/displayStrata?geological_group=Wangshi&group_formation_member=Wangshi Wangshi Group] {{Wayback|url=https://paleobiodb.org/classic/displayStrata?geological_group=Wangshi&group_formation_member=Wangshi |date=20211212203452 }} in the Paleobiology Database</ref>2010年左右，[[山东|山东]][[诸城|诸城]][[白垩纪|上白垩统]]的{{link-en|王氏群|Wangshi Group}}（确切来说是{{link-en|辛格庄组|Xingezhuang Formation}}<ref>Zhao Xijin, Wang Kebai, & Li Dunjing. (2011). "''[[华夏龙|Huaxiaosaurus aigahtens]]''." ''Geological Bulletin of China'' '''30''' (11):1671-1688</ref>）中出土了中国甲龙的[[正模标本|正模标本]]（'''ZJZ-183'''）。<ref>{{cite web|title=Shandong discovers new dinosaur with spikes!|url=http://www.yqqlm.com/2020/08/shandong-discovers-new-dinosaur-with-spikes/|publisher=yqqlm|access-date=21 August 2020|archive-date=2021-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211212203341/http://www.yqqlm.com/2020/08/shandong-discovers-new-dinosaur-with-spikes/|dead-url=no}}</ref>此化石在接下来的几年里准备完成，并在2020年被描述出来。<ref name=Wang2020 />

==叙述==
根据对[[绘龙|绘龙]]<ref>{{cite book |author=Gregory S. Paul |title=The Princeton Field Guide to Dinosaurs |publisher=Princeton University Press |place=United States of America |year=2010 |isbn=9780691137209|url=https://archive.org/details/princetonfieldgu0000paul }}</ref>――即诸城中国甲龙同时期亲缘动物的研究，后者体长将增加到{{conv|5|m|ft}}左右，体重不超过{{conv|2|tonnes|lb}}。<ref name=Wang2020 />

==古生态学==
中国甲龙发现于中国南部的辛格庄组，在其附近地层中发现的化石物种包括：[[中国角龙|中国角龙]]――一种[[角龙类|角龙类]]；<ref name=xu2010>{{Cite journal|author=Xu, X., Wang, K., Zhao, X. & Li, D.|year=2010|title=First ceratopsid dinosaur from China and its biogeographical implications|journal=Chinese Science Bulletin|volume=55|issue=16|pages=1631–1635|doi=10.1007/s11434-009-3614-5}}</ref>[[山东龙|山东龙]]――一种非常常见的[[鸭嘴龙类|鸭嘴龙类]]，当地的大部分化石皆归属于它；<ref name=xu2010/><ref name="hu1973"/>[[诸城暴龙|诸城暴龙]]――一种亚洲霸王龙类，与[[特暴龙|特暴龙]]具有亲缘关系；<ref name=xu2010/>[[诸城角龙|诸城角龙]]――一种亚洲纤角龙科；<ref name="zhao2007">{{cite journal|year=2007|title=''Zuchengosaurus maximus'' from Shandong Province|journal=Acta Geoscientia Sinica|volume=28|issue=2|pages=111–122|author1=Zhao, X. |author2=Li, D. |author3=Han, G. |author4=Zhao, H. |author5=Liu, F. |author6=Li, L. |author7=Fang, X.   |doi=10.1007/s10114-005-0808-x}}</ref>以及[[华夏龙|华夏龙]]――<ref name="zhao2011">{{cite journal|year=2011|title=''Huaxiaosaurus aigahtens''|journal=Geological Bulletin of China|volume=30|issue=11|pages=1671–1688|author1=Zhao X. |author2=Wang K. |author3=Li D.  }}</ref>化石可能是山东龙的较老个体，目前被视作后者的异名。<ref name="holtz2012">{{cite book|author=Holtz, T.R. Jr.|year=2012|title=Dinosaurs: The Most Complete, Up-to-Date Encyclopedia for Dinosaur Lovers of All Ages|url=https://archive.org/details/dinosaursmostcom00holt/page/47|publisher=Indiana University Press|isbn=978-0-375-82419-7|page=[https://archive.org/details/dinosaursmostcom00holt/page/47 47]|url-access=}}</ref><ref name="zhao2011"/>当地的其他可能残骸已分配至[[诸城龙|诸城龙]]属下，<ref name="zhao2007"/>而“诸城龙”也可能是山东龙的次异名，<ref name="holtz2012"/>材料暂时归类于[[暴龙|暴龙]]。<ref name="hu1973">{{cite journal|author=Hu, C.C.|year=1973|title=[A new hadrosaur from the Cretaceous of Chucheng, Shantung]|journal=Acta Geologica Sinica|volume=2|pages=179–206}}</ref>

